      },
      "lastUpdate": 1750201531172,
      "notes": "Start by creating a new project from the Home Screen. Select \"Design Freeform Haptics\" to begin.\n\n<p align=\"center\"> <img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/newproject.png\"/>\n\n\nYou can also combine freeform and audio clips within the same project.\nTo add a new freeform clip to an existing project, click the plus icon (+) in the Clip Navigator.\n\n<p align=\"center\"> <img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/addclip.png\"/>"
    },
    {
      "clipId": "da9f2546-48de-4b5c-bc9b-9b3d1cfd348a",
