      "lastUpdate": 1750201493361,
      "notes": "<p align=\"center\"> <img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/testing.png\"/>\n\nNow that you've created your haptic design, it's time to try it out!\n\nIf you haven’t already, connect your headset using the Connection Panel, then open the VR Companion App to test your designs.\n\nOnce you're satisfied with the result, you can export your design in the format of your choice for use in your project.\n\n\n\n/newpage\n\n<b>Congratulations!</b>\n\nYou've completed the  tutorial for freeform haptics using the Pen tool.\n\nFrom here, feel free to explore and experiment with the advanced features and capabilities of Haptics Studio. Happy creating!\n"
    }
